<td align="center"><a href="/wiki/Blackmail" title="Blackmail">Blackmail</a>, <a href="/wiki/Illegal_gambling" title="Illegal gambling" class="mw-redirect">Illegal gambling</a>, <a href="/wiki/Casino" title="Casino">Casino</a>, <a href="/wiki/Prostitution" title="Prostitution">Prostitution</a>, <a href="/wiki/Trafficking" title="Trafficking" class="mw-redirect">Trafficking</a></td>
