</table>
<p>The <b>Camorra</b> is a <a href="/wiki/Mafia" title="Mafia">mafia</a>-like <a href="/wiki/Organized_crime" title="Organized crime">criminal organization</a>, or <a href="/wiki/Secret_society" title="Secret society">secret society</a>, originating in the region of <a href="/wiki/Campania" title="Campania">Campania</a> and the city of <a href="/wiki/Naples" title="Naples">Naples</a> in <a href="/wiki/Italy" title="Italy">Italy</a>. It finances itself through drug trafficking, extortion, protection, and racketeering, and its activities have led to high levels of homicide in the areas in which it operates. It is the oldest organized criminal organization in Italy.</p>
